# ZizkaDB Infrastructure Conventions

## Local setup
```bash
bash scripts/setup-local.sh
# or: docker compose -f infra/docker-compose.yml -f infra/docker-compose.dashboard.yml up -d
```

## Services
| Service | Port | Image |
|---------|------|-------|
| Postgres+pgvector | 5432 | pgvector/pgvector:pg16 |
| Qdrant | 6333 | qdrant/qdrant |
| Redis | 6379 | redis:7-alpine |
| API | 8000 | `core/Dockerfile` |
| Dashboard | 3001 | `dashboard/Dockerfile` or PM2 |

## Production checklist
- `ENV=production`
- **Unset** `DEV_API_KEY`
- Strong `JWT_SECRET`, `JWT_REFRESH_SECRET`
- Configure `EMAIL_*` for OTP login
- `OPENAI_API_KEY` or tenant BYOK for embeddings
- nginx: `/v1/` → :8000, `/` → :3001 (`infra/nginx.conf`)

## Schema
- Init: `core/db/schema.sql` via Docker entrypoint
- Runtime ALTER: `core/db/connection.py` `init_db()`
- Migrations: `core/db/migrations/` — keep in sync with init_db

## Scripts
| Script | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `scripts/setup-local.sh` | One-command local stack |
| `scripts/smoke-test.sh` | Fast health + log smoke |
| `scripts/test-e2e-workflow.sh` | Full API workflow regression |
| `scripts/verify-release.sh` | Pre-push gate |
| `scripts/demo-why.py` | Causal chain demo |
| `infra/deploy-selfhost.sh` | PM2 dashboard deploy |

## Volumes
`postgres_data`, `qdrant_data`, `redis_data`, `community_uploads`
